data.description: Another quality build by Modern Homes, this 4-home community sits on a quiet street in Ballard not far from Market Street shops and restaurants. The location is rated "Very Walkable & Bikeable" on Walkscore with good transit and an easy commute into the city. Distinctive design features of the 820A floor plan include floating stairs, custom metal railings, sleek kitchen cabinets, and designer tile. The open concept living and dining area enjoys warm hardwoods, plenty of windows to maximize natural light and mini split for ultra-efficient heating and cooling. Two bedrooms share a full bath on the next level up and your lofty master suite has access to two rooftop deck areas.
